"シーです。"

#: ../../library/asyncio-policy.rst:131 ../../library/asyncio-policy.rst:139
msgid ":ref:`Availability <availability>`: Windows."
msgstr ":ref:`利用可能な環境 <availability>`: Windows 。"

#: ../../library/asyncio-policy.rst:136
